					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"凛", "Rin"},
					"“Ah, they’re probably asking how to tell them apart. Then it must be about the clothes. You can tell a girl from a boy when you see them.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"凛"},
					"“啊啊，是问如何分辨男女吧。应该写服装就可以了，看衣服也知道。”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"凛"},
					"「啊啊，是問如何分辨男女吧。應該寫服裝就可以了，看衣服也知道。」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0019_00128",
		linknext = "0019_00130",
